race.comment: Quick back up looks a good play with STEEL MOVE (3) who couldn't reel in the well-ridden winner last week but backed up the good Ballarat performance all the same and now finds a very similar - and very winnable - race. JUST FOR SHOW (1) didn't win last prep but ran a couple of good figures and copped a couple of bad rides on the way through. Peak ratings are the pick of what is on offer here. HARRY'S YACHT (2) has run well in both outings this time around and is a third up winner. TOROTENA (9) also arrives third up and along with HARRY'S YACHT filled the placings behind STEEL MOVE at Ballarat. They tie in and have to be respected. SILENT SHARES (7) returns having won around here fresh last prep and her jump out said that she was ready to go again.
